Class Dim3Specifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • cetus.hir.Specifier
      • omp2gpu.hir.Dim3Specifier
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Printable

    public class Dim3Specifier
extends Specifier
    Dim3Specifier represents an dim3 type specifier in CUDA, for example the round-bracketed parts of dim3 dimBlock(256,1,1);
